summary:
Armor Mod that adds a New Armor that a Lord of Cake May Wear
Made with ale at blacksmith
Use With Cake Lords Sword Mod

Story of the armor
It was forged in the land of cakes in a dying cake star
Using the Power of the Cake God (Me) this armor makes you basically invincible.
